# mbsync configuration — Gmail IMAP sync for mu4e
# Requires: Google App Password (not regular password)
# Create at: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# Store password in ~/.secrets/gmail_app_password
#
# First-time setup:
#   mbsync -a                    # initial full sync
#   mu init --maildir=~/Mail --my-address=omranaltunaiji@gmail.com
#   mu index

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User omranaltunaiji@gmail.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.secrets/gmail_app_password"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/Gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/Gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
